{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give a bonus to troops involved in the evacuation effort in Afghanistan",
        "additional_details": "I am ex Parachute Regiment and many of the troops out there are from the Parachute Regiment. And I want to do what I can for them as a veteran! Plus they 100% deserve it on top of the normal remuneration they receive.",
        "background": "I'd like the Government to provide a generous cash bonus to UK troops who have gone into Kabul on the Evacuation Mission, on their, I hope, safe return. This mission is of extreme danger and the Government should thank them monetarily.",
